<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbdfe1777-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s7264"><num value="7264">§ 7264.</num><heading> Seal of Department</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall cause a seal of office to be made for the Department of such design as he shall approve and judicial notice shall be taken of such seal.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbdfe1778-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/91/tVI/s654">Pub. L. 95–91, title VI, § 654</ref>, <date date="1977-08-04">Aug. 4, 1977</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/91/602">91 Stat. 602</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
